Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.CLI

Class CLI

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
it.polimi.ingsw.view.ClientView
it.polimi.ingsw.view.CLI.CLI
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Observer
public class CLI
extends ClientView
CLI is the command line interface of ClientView. inputThread constantly received System.in input from user. stdIn is the BufferedReader which buffer user input. receivedMessage is the last message received from Server. position is player's position in game. turn refers to if it's player's turn or not.
